{"tid":81672,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"自己約的炮含著淚也要打完","createTime":"2017-01-15T13:18:25.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-06T17:29:45.000Z","uid":17197,"like":12,"dislike":90,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d1e564807e2d967eb429b1892f1372bd9db434d9","tid":81672,"uid":17197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-15T13:18:25.000Z","msg":"【自己約的炮含著淚也要打完】<br />\n<br />\n日前，广西男子卢先生在网上认识了湖南新化女子小罗，双方迅速陷入网恋。<br />\n<br />\n两个多月后，卢先生从千里之外来到新化见网友，却发现梦寐以求的&ldquo;小萝莉&rdquo;矮而胖，与照片上的相差很远。<br />\n卢先生犹豫之下，还是硬着头皮和小罗去了宾馆。<br />\n在宾馆房间里，卢先生看到小罗洗完澡后的样子，心里实在无法接受这种反差，摔门而出。 <br />\n小罗也不是省油的灯，立即报警，声称被诈骗和非礼。<br />\n附近的警察马上赶到现场，在宾馆楼下的大堂里截住了卢先生。 <br />\n在听完双方的叙述后，警察建议卢先生继续和小罗约会，否则可能将以扰乱社会治安的罪名逮捕他。<br />\n最终在警察的注视下，卢先生含泪和小罗回到了 房间，做完了这场千里赴约的爱。<br />\n        <br />\n民警提示大家：约炮有风险，赴约需谨慎。<br />\n一旦赴约，请以一个成年人的标准要求自己。<br />\n<br />\n这就是所谓的&ldquo;自己约的炮，含泪也要打完&rdquo;？<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmesMpyAHMQ1Ngj7QzTbrtVd3e88aWnQKRznsa137g1KSQ?filename=k5o7MJz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fk5o7MJz.jpg&h=caf27b17&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmQpFsoGwu4YRf3KCNvtSSZ7QS4tcpC1YEeMSL8825xF4G?filename=52bu2va.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F52bu2va.jpg&h=a50c823c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmPchPBLdmXURjSMDhRqbU3F8wtauuB5U8azEPETL2V7rp?filename=7d7830O.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7d7830O.jpg&h=fabfb61e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/15/211758_eeafbabb52943c0cc45764ece94e5b3b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F15%2F211758_eeafbabb52943c0cc45764ece94e5b3b.jpg&h=de1ff7d4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmeBSvNPqvZ9m9mFxTVpwBAmZqUh1kXVdDq16GcVC3aSVN?filename=wabrjd5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fwabrjd5.jpg&h=6139ae2b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"da9bb79048bf1997dcfe6a0350498f7374b7b85a","tid":81672,"uid":17197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-15T13:19:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/15/211856_9009b25f374d3e172332472c9b63c6dc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F15%2F211856_9009b25f374d3e172332472c9b63c6dc.jpg&h=940b8201&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmeTzvK4S8JBn1HXbyQRBVUejxfnWa6XSotvXBgf3efnjp?filename=18S2711.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F18S2711.jpg&h=fffc4b4a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmQ7vVWjZWM9vUyRfupjP9mjkSPF8CcKPi79u5cLSjPv1y?filename=4m611QR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4m611QR.jpg&h=49f08ae7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"dd5c341122388bda6347c9447bf88aeef8418ffc","tid":81672,"uid":42735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-15T13:24:19.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">心</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"e839a2a8a572817f8ccb3004071cc76995be968a","tid":81672,"uid":3820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-15T13:25:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">心</span></strong></span></blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>理</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"64a70459f92cdd0f4b6fe41a05e07704b5965b7e","tid":81672,"uid":16036,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-15T13:26:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">心</span></strong></span></blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>理</strong></span></span>